flowchart TD
    SP[SharePoint Online<br/>Source of truth for submitted files<br/>Results CSVs written back]
    ING[Azure Function Ingestion<br/>Polls or detects new files<br/>Reads metadata only<br/>Groups by submission ID]
    SB[Azure Service Bus Queue<br/>Buffers work<br/>Smooths bursts<br/>Reduces pressure on SharePoint / Graph]
    ORCH[Azure Functions + Durable Functions<br/>Submission-level orchestrator]
    DI[Azure Document Intelligence<br/>OCR / text extraction]
    AOAI[Azure OpenAI<br/>Form classification<br/>Attachment classification<br/>Fact extraction]
    PY[Deterministic Validation Code<br/>Date windows<br/>Name matching<br/>Required document checks]
    BLOB[Azure Blob Storage<br/>Durable runtime state<br/>Optional temp artifacts<br/>Optional JSON audit results<br/>Optional YAML rule storage]
    OUT[SharePoint Online Results<br/>CSV by form type<br/>Business-facing output]

    SP -->|Metadata scan / file discovery| ING
    ING -->|Submission manifest| SB
    SB -->|Queued work item| ORCH
    ORCH -->|Fetch files on demand| SP
    ORCH --> DI
    ORCH --> AOAI
    DI --> ORCH
    AOAI --> ORCH
    ORCH --> PY
    PY --> ORCH
    ORCH --> BLOB
    ORCH --> OUT